metadata.name: Billing Services Group Limited
metadata.description: Billing Services Group Limited provides financial clearinghouse services for merchants, online stores, and telecommunications companies. It offers Wi-Fi solutions, including user access solutions, Wi-Fi estate management, and roaming services to mobile carriers and network operators; and VoiceLog, which provides third party voice verification and call recording services primarily to the telecommunications, cable, and utilities industries. The company also offers local exchange carrier phone clearing, billing, and settlement services to telecommunication providers; USBI that provides clearinghouse services, including billing, management, and reporting services for providers of residential and commercial long distance calls; and ZPDI, which offers clearinghouse services comprising billing, management, and reporting services for the operator services industry. Billing Services Group Limited was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in San Antonio, Texas.
